SYNOPSIS: A remake of the 1967 Richard Fleischer film of the same name, about an animal doctor whose patients&#039; barks, squeals, and meows turn into actual human voices, stirring up the practice. Now an adult, a near wreck stirs something in him and suddenly he can understand the animals again, whether he wants to or not.
